00:25:44,757 --> 00:25:46,497
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">ඔයාව සුභ උදෑසනක්.</font>

261
00:25:46,797 --> 00:25:47,537
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">සුභ උදෑසනක්.</font>

262
00:25:47,887 --> 00:25:50,527
<font face="LTFinnegan Medium" size="75" color="#f9f4f1">ඔබේ පාද වලට ආසන්නයි. එය හිමයි.</font>

